text:
Oh, I'm in the middle of washing dishes, and
my hands are all wet...! Just a moment, please...!
Seems like you can't let go of them...

Yes, thank you for calling!
This is 283PRO.

Yes, yes... Oh!
Thank you as always~. Ah, I see...

Yes, yes... Alright... Message received! Is there
anything else? Okay, thank you very much. Goodbye~.

The dry cleaner said your clothes are ready earlier
than expected, so please come pick them up~.

Sorry, and thank you...!
It felt like you're quite used to it.

Oh... Is that so...?
Maybe because I used to help out a lot.
